FBIS4-52366 "dreas090_i_94003" FBIS-EAS-94-090 Daily Report 10 May 1994 Cambodia Denies Daily's Dismissal Report Denies Daily's Dismissal Report BK1005061294 Bangkok BANGKOK POST (INSIDE INDOCHINA Supplement) in English 10 May 94 p 2 BK1005061294 Bangkok BANGKOK POST (INSIDE INDOCHINA Supplement) English BFN [Letter from Norodom Sirivut, secretary-general of FUNCINPEC, National United Front for an Independent, Neutral, Peaceful, and Cooperative Cambodia] [Text] I was astonished to read in the "INSIDE INDOCHINA" section of the Bangkok Post of May 3, 1994 the article written by aJean de Toulkork. I would like to clarify as follows: 1. HRH Samdech Krompreah Norodom Ranariddh, first prime minister of Cambodia and president of FUNCINPEC, never intended to fire or to dismiss me from the secretary-general of FUNCINPEC position. 2. I am myself, Samdech Kromkhun Norodom Sirivut, currently in the position of secretary-general of FUNCINPEC. I perform and continue to perform this duty and fulfill my responsibilities with the great support of Samdech Krompreah Norodom Ranariddh, the president. 3. In this capacity, as a secretary-general of the party, I serve and will serve the president, the party and the members of FUNCINPEC very faithfully. Norodom Sirivudh Secretary-General FUNCINPEC Phnom Penh
